Title: breaking bad
Plot: Nineteen-year-old Alice returns to the magical world from her childhood adventure, where she reunites with her old friends and learns of her true destiny: to end the Red Queen's reign of terror. Alice, an unpretentious and individual 19-year-old, is betrothed to a dunce of an English nobleman.
